name: Python Trier Meetup
description: This is a meet for anyone interested in learning or tinkering with Python.  All experience levels are welcome. We're also expanding our website at PythonTrier.com with more detail than we can put on the meetup page. We meet on the second Tuesday or every month in the Machinendeck Hackerspace in Trier, so come on out!
how_to_find_us: The building has a large "V" over the entrance. You can follow the signs to the beauty salon on the first floor. The meeting room is at the end of the hallway.
